398
00:20:58,509 --> 00:21:01,609
Ibu! Ibu!

399
00:21:03,809 --> 00:21:05,609
Ibu!

400
00:21:05,609 --> 00:21:08,209
Aku pulang, Mitsuru.

401
00:21:08,209 --> 00:21:11,609
Aku mengerti, ibunya mirip sepertimu, Azusa.

402
00:21:12,409 --> 00:21:14,109
Apa itu sebabnya dia mengirimiku surat?

403
00:21:15,509 --> 00:21:19,409
Istrimu dirawat tiga bulan karena tuberkulosis?

404
00:21:19,409 --> 00:21:22,509
Ya, kami tak ingin membuat Mitsuru cemas

405
00:21:22,509 --> 00:21:24,509
